¬In loving memory of
Sonja Arnold
1963-2018
Those who sow in tears will reap with songs of joy.
Those who go out weeping will return with songs
of joy, carrying sheaves with them.
Psalm 126"Ŕ
÷In loving memory of Peter Newens
1922-2010
My darling Peter I know that you are near
for still I hold your unseen hand your silent voice I hear.
Love forever Jane

Jane Newens
1921-2020
